                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220703-14-off68 t18220703-14-crimeloc71"></join>. On Thursday, the 6th of June, about a quarter before ten o'clock in the morning, I was in the back parlour at breakfast, and saw the prisoner come into the shop, take the hat, and run out. I pursued and took him two doors off with it under his arm.</p>
